    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Weekly Autoscaling Report </li>\n<li>Improve logs readability</li>\n<li>Remove support for IKEv1-L2TP from VPN module</li>\n<li>Log API routes currently being accessed using Basic Auth</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Database service isn't updating password secret properly</li>\n<li>500 error when list project network routes</li>\n<li>Fix upper and lower padding for /settings/vpn row</li>\n</ul>"
      },
